lead_paragraph: Andrew White III began his career at Kansas, then transferred to Nebraska and redshirted a year before playing another, only to wind up at Syracuse to finish off his unique college basketball odyssey.

headline.print_headline: Transfer Epidemic in College Hoops Has Coaches Concerned
